snippet.textDisplay:
The maestro gives it the best shot and produced a gem. Bagga and Rahat, both have a special musical bond I feel since mein tenu samjhawan.. Bagga did what he does usually, create magic. And the maestro raised the level once again emoting the devotional love and giving a modern sufi classic. Backing vocals complemented the music so beautifully. Salute to the whole team. And that Shehnai though, it was love.
Keep them coming.. Much love Coke Studio Pakistan.
